OL,3,C'He'd be very proud': Family of Hector
OL,4,CDuff mark 80th anniversary of D-Day
OL,6,FThe family of the Isle of Man's last
OL,7,Fremaining Normandy veteran have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to him to mark the 80th
OL,9,Fanniversary of .
OL,11,FHector Duff OBE died in 2020 at the
OL,12,Fage of 101, after spending his final
OL,13,Fyears talking in schools about his
OL,14,Ftime at war.
OL,16,FTo honour his memory his family
OL,17,Fgathered at the island's Normandy
OL,18,Fmemorial plaque in Douglas on 6 June
OL,19,Fto lay a wreath, in tribute.
