OL,4,CDuff mark 80th anniversary of D-Day
OL,6,FA number of events have been happening
OL,7,Faround the Isle of Man to mark the
OL,8,F80th anniversary of D-Day.
OL,10,FKey landmarks such as Douglas
OL,11,FPromenade, the Tower of Refuge, the
OL,12,FLegislative Buildings, Imperial
OL,13,FBuildings and Ramsey Swing Bridge will
OL,14,Fbe lit in red this evening.
OL,16,FChief Minister Alfred Cannan MHK said:
OL,17,F'The Isle of Man is proud to join the
OL,18,Fnation in commemorating the 80th
OL,19,Fanniversary of D-Day.
